entities.player_description:
(G) Total quantity of items if all slots are full
/ 100 to get the divisor to use to convert the current amount to percentage
(Normally you'd do G / qty * 100, but combinators can't do decimal so we need to do that bit earlier)

(G) Count of item if all slots were full (after we divided by 100 for easier percentage calcs)
R / G = Percentage full as decimal
